metadata.name: Memories Of Shawrma
metadata.description:
Wrapped in soft pita bread,  
Shawarma is a treat to be fed.  
Layers of meats and spices,  
So delicious, it entices.

Marinated for hours on end,  
The flavors blend and blend.  
Onions, tomatoes, and tahini,  
A symphony of flavors, mini.

Cooked on a spit, it turns,  
Juices and flavors it earns.  
A street food, a quick meal,  
But it always makes you feel.

So next time you're feeling peckish,  
Shawarma should be your dish.  
Tasty and satisfying,  
It's worth the trying.
